http://decocare.com</a> 裝修網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkdecoman.com/jsp/main.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkdecoman.com%2Fjsp%2Fmain.jsp&d=4dFubs1SaL5s%2BWI6%2Fcp113Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f6ac564a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkdecoman.com/jsp/main.jsp</a> 裝修佬 <br />\n<br />\n以上並非推薦<br />\n<br />\n按揭保險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkmc.com.hk/chi/our_business/mortgage_insurance_programme.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmc.com.hk%2Fchi%2Four_business%2Fmortgage_insurance_programme.html&d=4dFubs1SaL5s%2BWI6%2Fcp113Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=07332de6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkmc.com.hk/chi/our_business/mortgage_insurance_programme.html</a><br />\n<br />\n印花稅計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/stamp/stamp_duty_rates.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Ftaxes%2Fstamp%2Fstamp_duty_rates.htm&d=4dFubs1SaL5s%2BWI6%2Fcp113Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9a78dc58\" target=\"_blank\">http://gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/stamp/stamp_duty_rates.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男女朋友 可以未婚夫妻名義做按揭<br />\n<br />\n放租要5成按揭<br />\n<br />\ncash rebate 1% vs 1.x% <br />\n<br />\n簡單而言：例子買4m樓，借3.6m<br />\n<br />\n1. 手頭緊： 揀1%cash, loan size 借足 再extra 比1%cash （即 4mx0.6x1% = 24,000)<br />\n<br />\n2. 手頭唔緊： 揀回1.6%， 扣Loan size , 自己成交要比多1.6% 既錢 佢1個月內回返比你 變相同eg1 既loan size 少左 1.6%， 利息少D <br />\n（即 4m x 0.6x 1.6% = 38,400，比起例子1，你成交果陣暫時要比多38,400， 銀行一個月內退返比你）<br />\n<br />\nP.s : 每間銀行計法大致一樣，但都有唔同，例如IXBX, 佢既1.6係多過其他行，詳情問banker<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n置業POST 鐵三角<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225032_2c5cb87e1d5b576d5a3a71310d8e8e33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225032_2c5cb87e1d5b576d5a3a71310d8e8e33.jpg&h=7e6b4eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n置業POST 係時候加入林太敬拜環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225238_c2e09a7b5958bf79ab615df3c9244a48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225238_c2e09a7b5958bf79ab615df3c9244a48.jpg&h=1429f73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重溫經典<br />\n林太豪氣回應，「290萬已經最低，我個仔買貴40萬冇咩問題，佢要住㗎嘛，如果升又點呢。阿仔買嘅單位，銀行估到價，銀行唔會死錯人嘅，嗰啲咁既專家，食屎啦！我哋唔係有見地，我哋係腳踏實地，唔聽專家㗎，聽專家意見就死啦。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&d=4dFubs1SaL5s%2BWI6%2Fcp113Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3be50bbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&h=1154b792\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時係買樓時機？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225031_b0f1496fd73d036205628c24b24bb772.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225031_b0f1496fd73d036205628c24b24bb772.png&h=d72727b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225031_090360ff0b029b1f57ca40fe2926c68a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225031_090360ff0b029b1f57ca40fe2926c68a.png&h=54ca4a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立此存照, 置業POST 巴絲打同股榮對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n金管局有一個圖，不妨可借用供大家參考。該局根據差估處及統計處收集數據，以一個約500多呎單位的置業成本及租賃成本計算出買租價差比率，今年上半年比率達到176%，反映樓宇買家置業成本較租樓多出76%，1998年有關比率於300%以上見頂，然後急跌。2008年有關比率升至150%水平後，亦見頂急回。<br />\n過去兩年一直提示樓市有下跌風險，最終樓價指數反而升逾兩成。2018年預測，香港跟美國加息，樓價估計調整兩成，如明年底CCL最終不低於135（現為168），此欄及fb再不會再談任何樓市的相關資訊。<br />\n<br />\n股榮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1/posts/788073491376493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstockwing1%2Fposts%2F788073491376493&d=4dFubs1SaL5s%2BWI6%2Fcp113Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=0b1b72d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1/posts/788073491376493</a>"},{"pid":"1f6f7261e4b216e8587b41cf2488ac035939b2dc","tid":573171,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"【寵物，影音，入廚，家居就係樂趣多】低調置業討論區(123)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/571099/page/38?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/571099/page/38?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nLAST POST"},{"pid":"8078512a1e639b1193815ec86e0d4afe8240b662","tid":573171,"uid":42194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:09:40.000Z","msg":"原來開多左，浪巴果個吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}